{"pageNumber":451,"juzNumber":23,"verses":[{"key":"37:127","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":127,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":451,"arabicText":"فَكَذَّبُوهُ فَإِنَّهُمْ لَمُحْضَرُونَ","translationText":"And they denied him, so indeed, they will be brought [for punishment],"},{"key":"37:128","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":128,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":451,"arabicText":"إِلَّا عِبَادَ ٱللَّهِ ٱلْمُخْلَصِينَ","translationText":"Except the chosen servants of Allah."},{"key":"37:129","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":129,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":451,"arabicText":"وَتَرَكْنَا عَلَيْهِ فِى ٱلْءَاخِرِينَ","translationText":"And We left for him [favorable mention] among later generations:"},{"key":"37:130","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":130,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":451,"arabicText":"سَلَٰمٌ عَلَىٰٓ إِلْ يَاسِينَ","translationText":"\"Peace upon Elias.\""},{"key":"37:131","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":131,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":451,"arabicText":"إِنَّا كَذَٰلِكَ نَجْزِى ٱلْمُحْسِنِينَ","translationText":"Indeed, We thus reward the doers of good."},{"key":"37:132","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":132,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":451,"arabicText":"إِنَّهُۥ مِنْ عِبَادِنَا ٱلْمُؤْمِنِينَ","translationText":"Indeed, he was of Our believing servants."},{"key":"37:133","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":133,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":451,"arabicText":"وَإِنَّ لُوطًۭا لَّمِنَ ٱلْمُرْسَلِينَ","translationText":"And indeed, Lot was among the messengers."},{"key":"37:134","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":134,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":451,"arabicText":"إِذْ نَجَّيْنَٰهُ وَأَهْلَهُۥٓ أَجْمَعِينَ","translationText":"[So mention] when We saved him and his family, all,"},{"key":"37:135","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":135,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":451,"arabicText":"إِلَّا عَجُوزًۭا فِى ٱلْغَٰبِرِينَ","translationText":"Except his wife among those who remained [with the evildoers]."},{"key":"37:136","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":136,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":451,"arabicText":"ثُمَّ دَمَّرْنَا ٱلْءَاخَرِينَ","translationText":"Then We destroyed the others."},{"key":"37:137","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":137,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":451,"arabicText":"وَإِنَّكُمْ لَتَمُرُّونَ عَلَيْهِم مُّصْبِحِينَ","translationText":"And indeed, you pass by them in the morning"},{"key":"37:138","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":138,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":451,"arabicText":"وَبِٱلَّيْلِ ۗ أَفَلَا تَعْقِلُونَ","translationText":"And at night. Then will you not use reason?"},{"key":"37:139","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":139,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":451,"arabicText":"وَإِنَّ يُونُسَ لَمِنَ ٱلْمُرْسَلِينَ","translationText":"And indeed, Jonah was among the messengers."},{"key":"37:140","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":140,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":451,"arabicText":"إِذْ أَبَقَ إِلَى ٱلْفُلْكِ ٱلْمَشْحُونِ","translationText":"[Mention] when he ran away to the laden ship."},{"key":"37:141","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":141,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":451,"arabicText":"فَسَاهَمَ فَكَانَ مِنَ ٱلْمُدْحَضِينَ","translationText":"And he drew lots and was among the losers."},{"key":"37:142","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":142,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":451,"arabicText":"فَٱلْتَقَمَهُ ٱلْحُوتُ وَهُوَ مُلِيمٌۭ","translationText":"Then the fish swallowed him, while he was blameworthy."},{"key":"37:143","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":143,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":451,"arabicText":"فَلَوْلَآ أَنَّهُۥ كَانَ مِنَ ٱلْمُسَبِّحِينَ","translationText":"And had he not been of those who exalt Allah,"},{"key":"37:144","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":144,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":451,"arabicText":"لَلَبِثَ فِى بَطْنِهِۦٓ إِلَىٰ يَوْمِ يُبْعَثُونَ","translationText":"He would have remained inside its belly until the Day they are resurrected."},{"key":"37:145","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":145,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":451,"arabicText":"۞ فَنَبَذْنَٰهُ بِٱلْعَرَآءِ وَهُوَ سَقِيمٌۭ","translationText":"But We threw him onto the open shore while he was ill."},{"key":"37:146","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":146,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":451,"arabicText":"وَأَنۢبَتْنَا عَلَيْهِ شَجَرَةًۭ مِّن يَقْطِينٍۢ","translationText":"And We caused to grow over him a gourd vine."},{"key":"37:147","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":147,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":451,"arabicText":"وَأَرْسَلْنَٰهُ إِلَىٰ مِا۟ئَةِ أَلْفٍ أَوْ يَزِيدُونَ","translationText":"And We sent him to [his people of] a hundred thousand or more."},{"key":"37:148","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":148,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":451,"arabicText":"فَـَٔامَنُوا۟ فَمَتَّعْنَٰهُمْ إِلَىٰ حِينٍۢ","translationText":"And they believed, so We gave them enjoyment [of life] for a time."},{"key":"37:149","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":149,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":451,"arabicText":"فَٱسْتَفْتِهِمْ أَلِرَبِّكَ ٱلْبَنَاتُ وَلَهُمُ ٱلْبَنُونَ","translationText":"So inquire of them, [O Muhammad], \"Does your Lord have daughters while they have sons?"},{"key":"37:150","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":150,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":451,"arabicText":"أَمْ خَلَقْنَا ٱلْمَلَٰٓئِكَةَ إِنَٰثًۭا وَهُمْ شَٰهِدُونَ","translationText":"Or did We create the angels as females while they were witnesses?\""},{"key":"37:151","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":151,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":451,"arabicText":"أَلَآ إِنَّهُم مِّنْ إِفْكِهِمْ لَيَقُولُونَ","translationText":"Unquestionably, it is out of their [invented] falsehood that they say,"},{"key":"37:152","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":152,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":451,"arabicText":"وَلَدَ ٱللَّهُ وَإِنَّهُمْ لَكَٰذِبُونَ","translationText":"\" Allah has begotten,\" and indeed, they are liars."},{"key":"37:153","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":153,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":451,"arabicText":"أَصْطَفَى ٱلْبَنَاتِ عَلَى ٱلْبَنِينَ","translationText":"Has He chosen daughters over sons?"}],"translationEditionUsed":"en.sahih"}